  "instructions": [
    "1. In a large bowl, combine mixed greens, chwinamul leaves, and fresh mint leaves.",
    "2. Cut cherry tomatoes in half and add to the bowl.",
    "3. Thinly slice red onion and add to the bowl.",
    "4. In a small bowl, whisk together lemon juice and olive oil.",
    "5. Pour dressing over the salad and toss to combine.",
    "6. Sprinkle crunchy salad mix on top of the salad.",
    "7. Season with salt to taste.",
    "8. Cover and refrigerate for at least 30 minutes to allow flavors to meld.",
    "9. Serve chilled."
